reviewText: Nice little documentary.  If you are a resident of Northern KY or Cincinnati this is worth checking out.  After purchasing it, the DVD has made its rounds through my friends and family.  We all enjoyed it.

The video was interesting.  However, being familiar with the activities that were going on in Newport, I felt that it left out a lot of the interesting material.  It was good to see Johnny TV Peluso again.  He used to fix our TVs!
